des: WKXX 102.9 FM is Etowah County and East Alabama’s home for Classic Country favorites! Home for great classic country music, fun contests, news, and weather you need! We are always here when it comes to you. Learn more about us by visiting our website at wkxx.com. WKXX is based in Gadsden, Alabama.
